# Monitor System Metrics with Datadog

## Read Requests per Second
- Metric: `system.io.r_s`
- Host: 1300295-web-01
- Threshold: >100 reads/sec for 5 minutes
- Alert message: High disk read activity detected on host.

## Write Requests per Second
- Metric: `system.io.w_s`
- Host: 1300295-web-01
- Threshold: >100 writes/sec for 5 minutes
- Alert message: High disk write activity detected on host.
